11. Cherry-Pick Example (Using Git Graph)
Situation:

daily-report has a useful file:
best_git_practices.txt
You want this file in main

What you did:
Open Git Graph
Right-click commit "Added Git best practices"
Select Cherry-pick commit
Choose target branch: main

âœ” Result:
That file appears in main
Other report files remain excluded

